msgstr ""
"Executa :ref:`objetos aguardûÀveis <asyncio-awaitables>` na sequûˆncia *aws* "
"de forma *concorrente*."

#: ../../library/asyncio-task.rst:486
msgid ""
"If any awaitable in *aws* is a coroutine, it is automatically scheduled as a "
