msgstr ""
"Se ``gather()`` for *cancelado*, todos os aguardûÀveis que foram submetidos "
"(que nûÈo foram concluûÙdos ainda) tambûˋm sûÈo *cancelados*."

#: ../../library/asyncio-task.rst:504
msgid ""
"If any Task or Future from the *aws* sequence is *cancelled*, it is treated "
